We're too slow.

1529
02:17:06,483 --> 02:17:09,360
I am sorry. I cannot go faster.

1530
02:17:09,442 --> 02:17:11,360
I cannot move faster.

1531
02:17:12,360 --> 02:17:15,402
- Hey! Hey!
- Hey! Hey!

1532
02:17:18,442 --> 02:17:19,818
