1533
02:17:37,901 --> 02:17:39,110
Aahh!

1534
02:18:42,692 --> 02:18:43,817
Richard.

1535
02:18:46,110 --> 02:18:47,152
Help me.

1536
02:18:55,734 --> 02:18:58,943
I must rest. I cannot
go on any longer.

1537
02:18:59,692 --> 02:19:00,942
I must rest!

1538
02:19:02,235 --> 02:19:03,736
I'll carry her.

1539
02:19:44,859 --> 02:19:46,984
