02:24:30,692 --> 02:24:32,775
Mr. Ferguson, I'm Dr. Verden.

1571
02:24:33,110 --> 02:24:34,486
I told Conway you're coming.

1572
02:24:34,525 --> 02:24:37,567
- Oh good. This is my associate Theo Murphy.
- How do you do.

1573
02:24:37,650 --> 02:24:39,026
